 an air of determination. These two sisters, while distinct in their looks, share a graceful elegance that sets them apart in any room. ","#","^CLASS: lettrine ","/#","#","^didascalie","/#","\n","^DO: Fiordiligi, I can't believe it. Our beloved Guglielmo and Ferrando have been called to war. What are we going to do?","\n","^FI: I know, Dorabella. It's a dreadful situation. Our hearts ache for them. But we must stay strong.","\n","^DO: I can't help but worry, Fiordiligi. What if they don't come back? What if something terrible happens to them?","\n","^FI: We can't let fear consume us. We'll write them letters filled with love and encouragement. And while they're away, we'll keep their spirits alive by supporting one another and holding onto hope.","\n","^DO: You're right, Fiordiligi. We've faced challenges before, and we've always found a way through. Our love will endure, even in their absence.","\n","^FI: That's the spirit, dear sister. We'll stay strong together, just as they would want us to. And when this war is over, we'll be waiting here with open arms to welcome them back home.","\n","^DO: (Turning towards you) My Despina ! Finally you heard our cries of despair !","\n","ev",true,"/ev",{["VAR="] = "SisterFollow",["re"] = true},"ev",{["VAR?"] = "Despina"},{["f()"] = "RoomOf"},"/ev",{["VAR="] = "SisterDestination",["re"] = true},"\n",{"ev",{["VAR?"] = "Dorabella"},{["f()"] = "RoomOf"},{["VAR?"] = "Alfonso"},{["f()"] = "RoomOf"},"==",{["VAR?"] = "Fiordiligi"},{["f()"] = "RoomOf"},{["VAR?"] = "Alfonso"},{["f()"] = "RoomOf"},"==","&&","/ev",{{["->"] = ".^.b",["c"] = true},{["b"] = {"^ ",{["->"] = "flow",["var"] = true},{["->"] = ".^.^.^.14"},"TERM"}}},"nop","\n","ev",{["CNT?"] = ".^.c-2"},"/ev",{{["->"] = ".^.b",["c"] = true},{["b"] = {"^ ",{["->"] = ".^.^.^.^.^.follow_up"},{["->"] = ".^.^.^.20"},"TERM"}}},"nop","\n",{"ev","visit",3,"MIN","/ev","ev","du",0,"==","/ev",{["->"] = ".^.s0",["c"] = true},"ev","du",1,"==","/ev",{["->"] = ".^.s1",["c"] = true},"ev","du",2